<td valign="middle" align="left">|[[#Overall structure of CVS commands| &gt; ]]|</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left">|[[#Quick reference to CVS commands| &gt;&gt; ]]|</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left"> &nbsp; </td>
